  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study intends to determine if there is any difference in the occurrence of major adverse&#xD;
      cardiology events in patients discharged on the same day as their elective cardiac&#xD;
      angioplasty or discharged one day after their angioplasty.&#xD;
&#xD;
      Hypothesize that same day discharge is as safe as a day later discharge.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
